::Mosquitor::

Seeing Sniper start to run off, Mosquitor chases after him, ignoring the pain 
as the bullet hits him in the shoulder.

"DIE INTRUD-AAAAAAAHHHHHH!!!!!!!" the stupid insect gets to the charges just 
as they start to explode, sending him flying at an incredible speed back 
through the Predacon ship's door and slamming into a wall, the bot sliding 
down unconscious.
